@sarahcat21 One of the key reasons IMO for the tools mess today that makes "commoditizing ML" so hard is that tools builders must grapple with an ever moving target: 
- ML algos keep evolving.
- Appl. task variety & data modalities keep evolving.
- Persona (who does what) is still evolving.
